translation: Proceed to the next mission?{#Name=" "}
source: Proceed to the next mission?{#Name=" "}

translation: みんなで一つの場所に集まるデモ{#Name=" "}
source: みんなで一つの場所に集まるデモ{#Name=" "}

translation: Hmm... I can feel it. Yeees. Feeeeeel it.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Hmm... I can feel it. Yeees. Feeeeeel it.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Not now, Octa. I've got a headache.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Not now, Octa. I've got a headache.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh ho! No, my lady—for once, my thoughts are elsewhere.{LF}This time...I have a feeling Mikhail has been cursed.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Oh ho! No, my lady—for once, my thoughts are elsewhere.{LF}This time...I have a feeling Mikhail has been cursed.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: You think a curse is responsible for his devolution?{#Name="Decadus"}
source: You think a curse is responsible for his devolution?{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Son of a... Then who's the bastard responsible?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Son of a... Then who's the bastard responsible?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Well, lemme think... Hmmm... HMMM...{#Name="Dito"}
source: Well, lemme think... Hmmm... HMMM...{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Oh, I dunno. Maybe...{LF}THE INTONER WE'VE BEEN TRYING TO KILL!?{#Name="Dito"}
source: Oh, I dunno. Maybe...{LF}THE INTONER WE'VE BEEN TRYING TO KILL!?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Two... I'm gonna crush her!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Two... I'm gonna crush her!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Now, now, even I take a break from fleshly pursuits{LF}from time to time. {#Name="Octa"}
source: Now, now, even I take a break from fleshly pursuits{LF}from time to time. {#Name="Octa"}

translation: Huh. Yes. Fascinating. I think I may have been{LF}with Lady Two sometime in the past.{#Name="Cent"}
source: Huh. Yes. Fascinating. I think I may have been{LF}with Lady Two sometime in the past.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I had some kind of role with her.{LF}Like a servant. Or perhaps a butler.{#Name="Cent"}
source: I had some kind of role with her.{LF}Like a servant. Or perhaps a butler.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Or a disciple, maybe?{#Name="Dito"}
source: Or a disciple, maybe?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Oh yeah?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Oh yeah?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Well, I suppose you could kind of, sort of, maybe say that?{#Name="Cent"}
source: Well, I suppose you could kind of, sort of, maybe say that?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Where is Lady Two now?{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Where is Lady Two now?{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: How on earth would I know?{#Name="Cent"}
source: How on earth would I know?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I last saw her in the desert ruins, buuut...{LF}goodness, that was ages upon ages ago. {#Name="Cent"}
source: I last saw her in the desert ruins, buuut...{LF}goodness, that was ages upon ages ago. {#Name="Cent"}

translation: Why'd you leave her?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Why'd you leave her?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh, you know! Every bird has to soar from{LF}the cage of iniquity and...things.{#Name="Cent"}
source: Oh, you know! Every bird has to soar from{LF}the cage of iniquity and...things.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I don't understand half the crap you say.{#Name="Zero"}
source: I don't understand half the crap you say.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Goodness. I haven't uttered the name{LF}"Lady Two" in quite some time...{#Name="Cent"}
source: Goodness. I haven't uttered the name{LF}"Lady Two" in quite some time...{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Hey, Mikhail! You're more of a big baby now than ever, huh?{#Name="Dito"}
source: Hey, Mikhail! You're more of a big baby now than ever, huh?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: There is no need for such cruelty, Dito.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: There is no need for such cruelty, Dito.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Am I back to being useless?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Am I back to being useless?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Not at all. You just need rest.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Not at all. You just need rest.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Bleh. You're makin' me puke over here!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Bleh. You're makin' me puke over here!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Empty sympathy like that just ends up{LF}making people feel worse.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Empty sympathy like that just ends up{LF}making people feel worse.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: I was freezin' to death earlier, but did anyone{LF}worry about ol' Dito? Noooooo...{#Name="Dito"}
source: I was freezin' to death earlier, but did anyone{LF}worry about ol' Dito? Noooooo...{#Name="Dito"}

translation: This is all a tad worrisome.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: This is all a tad worrisome.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: What is?{#Name="Zero"}
source: What is?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: The situation with poor Mikhail...{#Name="Decadus"}
source: The situation with poor Mikhail...{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: I feel for you, my lady. I will do all in my power to save Mikhail.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: I feel for you, my lady. I will do all in my power to save Mikhail.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Zero, I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Zero, I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Quit apologizing. If you feel bad about it, just get better.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Quit apologizing. If you feel bad about it, just get better.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Okay. I want to be better, Zero.{LF}Better and stronger. I really do.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Okay. I want to be better, Zero.{LF}Better and stronger. I really do.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: I hate being weak like this...{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I hate being weak like this...{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: I just want to protect you, Zero. I really, really hate this!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I just want to protect you, Zero. I really, really hate this!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: ...Go to sleep.{#Name="Zero"}
source: ...Go to sleep.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I'm sorry. ...I'm really sorry.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I'm sorry. ...I'm really sorry.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: It's time to go.{#Name="Zero"}
source: It's time to go.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Very well. We must find Lady Two as soon as we can.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Very well. We must find Lady Two as soon as we can.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: You stay here and rest.{#Name="Zero"}
source: You stay here and rest.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I'm sorry, everyone.{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I'm sorry, everyone.{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Oh ho! What is there for you to apologize for?{#Name="Octa"}
source: Oh ho! What is there for you to apologize for?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: You know, now that you mention it...{#Name="Cent"}
source: You know, now that you mention it...{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Trivia time! Did you know apologies were{LF}once known as "the false gold of sinners"?{#Name="Cent"}
source: Trivia time! Did you know apologies were{LF}once known as "the false gold of sinners"?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Yeah, yeah. Just shut up, would you?{LF}Come on, Zero, let's get outta here.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Yeah, yeah. Just shut up, would you?{LF}Come on, Zero, let's get outta here.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: こんなクソみたいな砂漠で迷うとは……{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: こんなクソみたいな砂漠で迷うとは……{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: It's time to go.{#Name="Zero"}
source: It's time to go.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Very well. We must find Lady Two as soon as we can.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Very well. We must find Lady Two as soon as we can.{#Name="Decadus"}

source: Zero...{#Name="Mikhail"}
